2004-05-10  Darin Adler  <darin@apple.com>

        Reviewed by Vicki.

        - fixed build failure seen in B&I log (due to case sensitive file system?)

        * kwq/KWQLoader.h: Include "KWQCString.h" rather than "QCString.h". The latter was
